item.title: PostgreSQL 16
item.description: The extensions listed are included in the standard images. This list refers to PostgreSQL 16. Name Default Version Comment adminpack 2.1 Administrative functions for PostgreSQL amcheck 1.3 Functions for verifying relation integrity autoinc 1.0 Functions for autoincrementing fields bloom 1.0 Bloom access method - signature file based index btree_gin 1.3 Support for indexing common datatypes in GIN btree_gist 1.7 Support for indexing common datatypes in GiST citext 1.6 Data type for case-insensitive character strings credcheck 2.
